snippet.title: Reign of Guilds - pre-Alpha sneak peek
snippet.description: Here's a short sneak peek of a new combat system in Reign of Guilds. Currently, we're in an active stage of PvP testing and debugging at our development PTR. Get ready to see more of a new combat system with detailed description of new features soon.
